import React from 'react'
import { Routes } from 'react-router-dom'
import Nav from './Pages/Nav'

const Route = () => {
  return (
        <>
            <Nav/>
            <Routes>
        <Route path='/' element={<Home />} />
        <Route path='/about' element={<About />} />
        <Route path='/cart' element={<CartPage />} />
      </Routes>
        </>
  )
}

export default Route
